sheldon bergstrom is a canadian film , television and stage actor . in 2014 , it was announced that he had been cast as rob ford in factory theatre 's upcoming production of rob ford : the musical . originally from prince albert , saskatchewan , he is currently based in regina . his other roles have included edna turnblad in hairspray , franz in the producers , horton in seussical and mr. bumble in oliver , as well as guest appearances in episodes of corner gas and insecurity . he is also a frequent host of telemiracle telethons in saskatchewan .